branchCategory.description:
&lt;p&gt;
The NCRB single vane, double shaft style rotary actuator is available in 7 sizes (10-30mm). Rotation angles of up to 270&#xb0; is possible for the entire series. The NCRB series offers smooth, step-free operation and long life expectancies in rugged service applications. Optional auto switches are available.
&lt;/p&gt;

